      "para_id": "Q004386.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) Šu-Suen , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters : Hulal , the scribe , child of Šu-Iškur , the equerry , is your servant ."
    }
